claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: Page header of an original article showing the title “Recombinant or Standard-Dose Influenza Vaccine in Adults under 65 Years of Age” and a list of authors; no data or statements about antigenic matching are included. does not support the claim because the image is only the article title page and contains no information on antigenic match with WHO- or FDA-selected strains. Note: Image is a title page without relevant data; resolution is sufficient to confirm absence of supporting evidence.
